extendedInfo.description: Seadoo Dealer, Sussex Marine Watersports is a Uk Seadoo Dealer in the South of England, on the A259 between Brighton and Worthing. This FREE App is for all lovers of Seadoo Jetski's, Shows all the Current Range Available in the UK, Prices and Special Offers. Be the first people to see the following years ski's as soon as we have the information. Also see our full range of used and Brokerage Ski's available. Even if your not interested in buying your own Jetski then this app is worth it just to find out what new jet skis are coming next year! Most information from our website is all compacted into one single application which you can access anywhere.

reviews.comment: Great app found my new ski on here!
